article_title: Jordan summons Iran ambassador over remarks.
sentence: Jordan,  which  has  a  peace  treaty  with  Israel,  has  been  highly  critical  of  the  way  Israel  has  carried  out  its  campaign  against  Hamas  in  Gaza,  which  has  killed  33,000  mainly  civilians,  according  to  the  Hamas-run  Gaza  ministry  of  health.
